{"tid":158409,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"小心中招！WhatsApp 及 Telegram 新漏洞可令黑客完全控制帳戶","createTime":"2017-03-16T08:53:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T14:43:53.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a72c59b2eda99a73d8145764a19b618b0dcdb83f","tid":158409,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T08:53:42.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">小心中招！WhatsApp 及 Telegram 新漏洞可令黑客完全控制帳戶<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/03/16/vulnerability-allowed-hackers-to-take-over-whatsapp-and-telegram-accounts/software/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F03%2F16%2Fvulnerability-allowed-hackers-to-take-over-whatsapp-and-telegram-accounts%2Fsoftware%2F&d=ekRw3fL0jih6ME0SbOEd76S6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=8b4b29af\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/03/16/vulnerability-allowed-hackers-to-take-over-whatsapp-and-telegram-accounts/software/</a></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n今時今日任何系統及程式出現漏洞往往是在所難免，而黑客亦經常會利用這些漏洞去進行攻擊。最近安全機構 Check Point 就宣佈 WhatsApp 及 Telegram 又出現類似問題，黑客會透過看似沒有問題的相片及影片去引導用戶下載惡意軟件，成功的話即可完全接管受害者的帳戶。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/001-87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F001-87.jpg&h=65776ab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據 Check Point 產品漏洞研究主管 Oded Vanunu 表示，黑客今次採用的是一種司空見慣的攻擊手法。透過 WhatsApp 及 Telegram 上出現的新漏洞，黑客會先向目標人士發送一張看似正常的相片，但內裡卻其實暗藏惡意代碼。以 WhatsApp 為例，當用戶打開相關圖片，即會被引導到一個含有惡意軟件的 HTML 頁面，一旦加載黑客即能劫持用戶帳戶。至於該漏洞在 Telegram 上則較難以利用，因為用戶需要在 Chrome 新分頁上運行一段影片，而 Telegram 表示這種睇片方式並不尋常。<br />\n<br />\nCheck Point 已於 3 月 8 日向 WhatsApp 及 Telegram 報告上述漏洞，而兩者目前已經修正了文件上傳操作驗證，以防止黑客再次有機可乘。由於今次這項漏洞出現在舊版本上，而官方已經在更新中進行修復，為避免意外中招，建議各位應盡快更新至最新版本，當然切勿胡亂開啟來歷不明的相片、影片、文件及連結亦是最大效的保護措施。"},{"pid":"2bfc7e82039be4a2c24f62ec5af3d0a8eb3fdf8d","tid":158409,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a68d2bc6bb0175ba3dde3b9cb0c1e579ebfaf3d","tid":158409,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:48:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71872a80522a90e88cf309d924a08b92b4774e06","tid":158409,"uid":25147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:57:28.000Z","msg":"毒撚: 我wtsap會唔會比人hack左，好耐無響過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a01727dbc92de807e186a9c899926d27f5e0a2f","tid":158409,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:58:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7baf8ea0c3d3c7f2521d2c99a1141beeaa7b0cc7","tid":158409,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:34:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c53182a3b5fc4d4a99c16d4f7b4b243099c6c26","tid":158409,"uid":51066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:37:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毒撚: 我wtsap會唔會比人hack左，好耐無響過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無響過其實係連畀人hack嘅價值都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569028ec49a703ad63902343b574ba09c1bda0bf","tid":158409,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:43:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}